to-break-call-of-duty-sales-stranglehold-3558925">broke <em>Call Of Duty</em> ’s four-year run</a> at the top and was the first game not developed by either Activision Blizzard or Rockstar to top the best-selling list since 2008. <em>Call Of Duty</em> games have been the best selling titles in America for 13 of the past 16 years, with <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-v">Grand Theft Auto 5</a></em> and <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/red-dead-redemption-2">Red Dead Redemption 2</a></em> topping the charts in 2013 and 2018 respectively. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="第02季发射预告片|使命召唤：Warzone＆Black Ops 6" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SXpnKJBhL48?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> If Rockstar does release the long-awaited <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-vi">Grand Theft Auto 6</a></em> in 2025, it&#39;s likely to be the best-selling game of this year. According to the latest rumours, news about release dates <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/grand-theft-auto-6-rumour-release-date-trailer-3831054">could be revealed next week</a> . It&#39;s also been reported a number of other game studios are <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unknown-gta-6-release-date-is-causing-delays-with-rival-games-3820798#:~:text=All%20we%20know%20about%20GTA,games%20far%2C%20far%20away.%E2%80%9D">delaying their games</a> to ensure they don&#39;t clash with the sequel.</p><p> <em>Call Of Duty: Black Ops 6</em> ’s <a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-season-2-release-date-3813180">season two</a> launches next week (January 28) and introduces new multiplayer maps, weapons and a Terminator crossover to the game.</p><p> In other news, the last instalment in 